<script>
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.vue";
import PageHeader from "@/components/page-header";

export default{
    components: {
        Layout,
        PageHeader
    },
    data(){
        return{
            title: "Rapport de consultation",
            items: [
                {
                    text: "Tableau de bord",
                    href: "/",
                },
                {
                    text: "Editions",
                    href: "/",
                },
                {
                    text: "rapport de consultation",
                    active: true,
                },
            ],
        }
    }

}
</script>
<template>
    <Layout>
        <PageHeader :title="title" :items="items" />

    </Layout>
</template>
